response.overview: A young girl, passionate about fashion design, is mysteriously able to enter the 1960s where she encounters her idol, a dazzling wannabe singer. But 1960s London is not what it seems, and time seems to be falling apart with shady consequences.
response.tagline: When the past lets you in, the truth will come out.
response.title: Last Night in Soho
